Stellar parameters
------------------

Many of the stellar parameters are taken from Allen (2000), specifically
Chapter 15. The radii for M giants are taken from the following paper:

    http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1998NewA....3..137D

Cohen 1994
----------

 - Added L' spur towards Galactic center
 - Both spurs are 300pc wide instead of 750pc

Cohen 1995
----------

 - Changed g_h from 0.002 to 0.0008
